---
import Badge from "./Badge.astro";
---

<section class="section section__offerings container" data-gsap-trigger data-gsap-animate>
    <div class="offerings-card">
        <div class="offerings-card__img">
            <span class="offerings-card__icon">
                <svg role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <title>Icono de tendencia subiendo</title>
                    <path
                        d="M3.4 18L2 16.6L7.3 11.3C7.88333 10.7167 8.59167 10.425 9.425 10.425C10.2583 10.425 10.9667 10.7167 11.55 11.3L12.7 12.45C12.9 12.65 13.1375 12.75 13.4125 12.75C13.6875 12.75 13.925 12.65 14.125 12.45L18.575 8H16V6H22V12H20V9.425L15.525 13.875C14.9417 14.4583 14.2333 14.75 13.4 14.75C12.5667 14.75 11.8583 14.4583 11.275 13.875L10.1 12.7C9.91667 12.5167 9.68333 12.425 9.4 12.425C9.11667 12.425 8.88333 12.5167 8.7 12.7L3.4 18Z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
            </span>
        </div>
        <div class="section__paragraph">
            <h3 class="h3">Protejete contra la inflación.</h3>
            <p class="h3">Mantenemos tu dinero en USDT para que puedas estar seguro sabiendo que el valor del precio siempre estará vinculado 1 a 1 al dólar americano.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="label-small">1 USDT ~ 1,00 USD</p>
    </div>
    <div class="offerings-card">
        <div class="offerings-card__img">
            <span class="offerings-card__icon">
                <svg role="img" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <title>Icono de cochinito ahorrador</title>
                    <path
                        d="M16 11C16.2833 11 16.5208 10.9042 16.7125 10.7125C16.9042 10.5208 17 10.2833 17 10C17 9.71667 16.9042 9.47917 16.7125 9.2875C16.5208 9.09583 16.2833 9 16 9C15.7167 9 15.4792 9.09583 15.2875 9.2875C15.0958 9.47917 15 9.71667 15 10C15 10.2833 15.0958 10.5208 15.2875 10.7125C15.4792 10.9042 15.7167 11 16 11ZM8 9H13V7H8V9ZM4.5 21C3.93333 19.1 3.375 17.2042 2.825 15.3125C2.275 13.4208 2 11.4833 2 9.5C2 7.96667 2.53333 6.66667 3.6 5.6C4.66667 4.53333 5.96667 4 7.5 4H12.5C12.9833 3.36667 13.5708 2.875 14.2625 2.525C14.9542 2.175 15.7 2 16.5 2C16.9167 2 17.2708 2.14583 17.5625 2.4375C17.8542 2.72917 18 3.08333 18 3.5C18 3.6 17.9875 3.7 17.9625 3.8C17.9375 3.9 17.9083 3.99167 17.875 4.075C17.8083 4.25833 17.7458 4.44583 17.6875 4.6375C17.6292 4.82917 17.5833 5.025 17.55 5.225L19.825 7.5H22V14.475L19.175 15.4L17.5 21H12V19H10V21H4.5ZM6 19H8V17H14V19H16L17.55 13.85L20 13.025V9.5H19L15.5 6C15.5 5.66667 15.5208 5.34583 15.5625 5.0375C15.6042 4.72917 15.6667 4.41667 15.75 4.1C15.2667 4.23333 14.8417 4.4625 14.475 4.7875C14.1083 5.1125 13.8417 5.51667 13.675 6H7.5C6.53333 6 5.70833 6.34167 5.025 7.025C4.34167 7.70833 4 8.53333 4 9.5C4 11.1333 4.225 12.7292 4.675 14.2875C5.125 15.8458 5.56667 17.4167 6 19Z"
                        fill="#003733"></path>
                </svg>
            </span>
            <Badge>Pronto</Badge>
        </div>
        <div class="section__paragraph">
            <h3 class="h3">Genera ingresos con compras en la tienda NFT.</h3>
            <p class="h3">Cada pieza de activo digital 3D que compres, vendas o conserves genera una pequeña utilidad de interés, cuanto más raro sea el objeto, mayores serán tus ganancias.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section__offerings {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .offerings-card {
        display: grid;
        gap: 24px;
        padding: 40px 24px 40px 24px;
        border-radius: 32px;
        background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, rgb(var(--md-ref-neutral17)) -60%, rgb(var(--md-ref-neutral17) / 0));

        .offerings-card__img {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;

            .offerings-card__icon {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                width: 36px;
                height: 36px;
                border-radius: 9999px;
                color: var(--md-sys-color-on-tertiary);
                background-color: var(--md-sys-color-tertiary);

                svg {
                    fill: currentColor;
                }
            }
        }

        @media (width >= 768px) {
            & {
                padding: 70px 48px 70px 48px;
            }
        }

        @media (width >= 992px) {
            & {
                padding-inline: 64px;
            }
        }
    }
</style>
